  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nWhen calling the api for beacon block, there is a one-off bug for the slot:\r\n\r\nex:\r\nreq:\r\n```\r\ncurl -X 'GET' \\\r\n  '<IP>:<PORT>/eth/v1/beacon/blocks/2900001/attestations' \\\r\n  -H 'accept: application/json'\r\n```\r\nresp:\r\n```\r\n{\"data\":[{\"aggregation_bits\":\"0xf7bf7abffffdef3f\",\"data\":{\"slot\":\"2900000\",\"index\":\"0\",\"beacon_block_root\":\"0xa86af90be36050734820488d53ca34dd10adf905e47ad54112bacb17af32c5a8\",\"source\":{\"epoch\":\"90624\",\"root\":\"0xb7ad9f6f961336a2eae59fe283204a22c6126543804cab3273068768afdffa7e\"},\"target\":{\"epoch\":\"90625\",\"root\":\"0xa86af90be36050734820488d53ca34dd10adf905e47ad54112bacb17af32c5a8\"}},\"signature\":\"0x91ee211c9672868eec4e9bb899a0b4885f2b7a4e8806820d2ef6fb719bc162726d13d8f5a9c8fc3c25a9824530a9caca03619aae8c9db25449bc5560fada18a22da808ae50cdc68e6f04cbaad832c7ee16848ebd75bdbd6bac45a56603ce5366\"}],\"execution_optimistic\":false}\r\n```\r\n\r\n^as can be seen above, the slot i have provided is `2900001` but the slot returned is `2900000` in the data.slot field.\r\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nI would expect that the slot provided would be the slot returned. however, if this is expected behavior, then this issue ticket can be ignored and closed.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. call open api endpoint of consensus client:\r\n```\r\n curl -X 'GET' \\\r\n  '<IP>:<PORT>/eth/v1/beacon/blocks/2900001/attestations' \\\r\n  -H 'accept: application/json'\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\nv1.9.2/26fd079",
